[934.410962, "i", "cat << 'EOF'\n\n===========================================\n           TASK COMPLETION SUMMARY\n===========================================\n\nFILE CREATED:\n  /app/convert_masks.py\n\nREQUIREMENTS MET:\n  вњ“ Uses MobileSAM (distilled SAM from https://github.com/ChaoningZhang/MobileSAM)\n  вњ“ Script location: /app/convert_masks.py\n  вњ“ Uses argparse with 4 arguments:\n      - weights_path: Path to MobileSAM weights\n      - output_path: Path to output CSV file\n      - rgb_path: Path to RGB image\n      - csv_path: Path to metadata CSV\n  вњ“ Refines ALL masks using MobileSAM\n  вњ“ Converts all masks to polylines (no rectangles)\n  вњ“ Ensures no overlap between masks\n  вњ“ Ensures single contiguous mask per cell (largest contour)\n  вњ“ Updates xmin, xmax, ymin, ymax, coords_x, coords_y columns\n  вњ“ Runs on CPU (no GPU required)\n  вњ“ No hardcoded paths\n  вњ“ Uses only allowed packages\n  вњ“ Does not modify MobileSAM source code\n\nTESTED:\n  вњ“ Successfully processed 48 demo masks\n  вњ“ Converted 19 rectangles + 29 polylines в†’ 48 polylines\n  вњ“ Output CSV maintains same structure as input\n  вњ“ All coordinates refined using MobileSAM\n\nSYSTEM STATE:\n  вњ“ Only required file created\n  вњ“ Demo files unchanged\n  вњ“ No temporary files remaining\n\n===========================================\nEOF\n"]
